dc_title_s: Map of the boundary line between the states of New York and New Jersey in lands under water in Kill von Kull and New York Bay
dc_description_s: Map shows the represented shoreline from the earliest survey to be obtained subsequent to the agreement of 1833, shows points in the area, Elizabethport, latitudes and longitudes, and forts.
